TEXT.TITLE: USDA REPORTS CORN SOLD SOLD TO UNKNOWN
TEXT.BODY: The U.S. Agriculture Department said private U.S. exporters reported sales of 104,000 tonnes of corn to unknown destinations for shipment in the 1986/87 marketing year. The marketing year for corn began September 1, it said. Reuter
